(5, 1, 'Professional Certificate in UI/UX Design', 'UI-101', 22000, '<p><font color=\"#000000\"><b>This course is suited to anybody interested in designing beautiful interfaces for digital products.</b></font></p>', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; background-image: none !important; background-position: 0px 0px !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: repeat !important; background-attachment: scroll !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">About this Course</strong></p><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;\">In this course, you will gain an understanding of the critical importance of user interface design. You will also learn industry-standard methods for how to approach the design of a user interface and key theories and frameworks that underlie the design of most interfaces you use today.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;\">Through a series of case studies on commercial systems - many of which you likely use on a regular basis - we will illustrate the benefits of good design. We will also demonstrate how the costs of bad design can often be severe (in user experience, money, and even human lives).<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;\">You will then gain a high-level understanding of the user-interface design process. You will be introduced to common design scenarios - e.g. improving on existing designs and starting a new design from scratch - and the general design processes that tend to be used for each scenario.<br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></div><div style=\"box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify;\">Finally, we will begin introducing the large body of existing knowledge on design by providing overviews of core user interface design theories and concepts. This key foundational information will help you avoid reinventing the wheel when you are designing your interfaces in this specialization.</div><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; background-image: none !important; background-position: 0px 0px !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: repeat !important; background-attachment: scroll !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">What will you learn?</strong></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; background-image: none !important; background-position: 0px 0px !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: repeat !important; background-attachment: scroll !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">By earning this certification, you will be able to:</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Influence peoples perceptions of a product through UI design.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; background-image: none !important; background-position: 0px 0px !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: repeat !important; background-attachment: scroll !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Interpret the tone and personality of a products brand and convey that throughout the UI.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; background-image: none !important; background-position: 0px 0px !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: repeat !important; background-attachment: scroll !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Systematically and consistently use sizing, spacing, alignment, and other systems to bring a sense of order to designs.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; background-image: none !important; background-position: 0px 0px !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: repeat !important; background-attachment: scroll !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Design for different screen sizes, from responsive desktop to native mobile.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; background-image: none !important; background-position: 0px 0px !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: repeat !important; background-attachment: scroll !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Instantly spot common mistakes and articulate them to others with a sharpened sense of what makes good UI work.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; background-image: none !important; background-position: 0px 0px !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: repeat !important; background-attachment: scroll !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Give accurate feedback on UI designs with the vocabulary and skills to action them.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; background-image: none !important; background-position: 0px 0px !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: repeat !important; background-attachment: scroll !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Establish and apply best practice workflows from low fidelity ideation to high fidelity designs.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; background-image: none !important; background-position: 0px 0px !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: repeat !important; background-attachment: scroll !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Understand the role of animation in UI and use animations and transitions effectively in your designs.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; background-image: none !important; background-position: 0px 0px !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: repeat !important; background-attachment: scroll !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Design your interface with intent and articulate your decisions and rationale to others.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; background-image: none !important; background-position: 0px 0px !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: repeat !important; background-attachment: scroll !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Present your work in the most effective way.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; background-image: none !important; background-position: 0px 0px !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: repeat !important; background-attachment: scroll !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Ask for and handle feedback.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; background-image: none !important; background-position: 0px 0px !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: repeat !important; background-attachment: scroll !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Communicate confidently with stakeholders, such as developers, product managers, quality assurance testers and clients throughout the design process.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; background-image: none !important; background-position: 0px 0px !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: repeat !important; background-attachment: scroll !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">Prepare your files for handover to developers.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; background-image: none !important; background-position: 0px 0px !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: repeat !important; background-attachment: scroll !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: justify; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: 700;\">This course is suited to anybody interested in designing beautiful interfaces for digital products.</strong><br style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Graphic designers and digital designers who want to up skill to UI design.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 20px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); outline: none; text-decoration: none; font-size: 16px; font-weight: 300; font-family: Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 21px; background-image: none !important; background-position: 0px 0px !important; background-size: initial !important; background-repeat: repeat !important; background-a